              to 25 percent (subject to certain limitations and maximums) midway
              through the season. The sides also agreed that beginning in 2020-21,
              the escrow withholding will increase to 20% for the remainder of the
              term of the CBA, and if the total escrow withholding is insufficient,
              it will be funded from the escrow withholdings in the two subsequent
              seasons.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
